zathura is the pdf/djvu reader.
    h/j/k/l - Move left/down/up/right in document
    d/u - Down/up a half page
    g - Top of document
    G - Bottom of document
    i - Toggle dark mode
    b - Toggle statusbar
    f - Highlight URLS to follow
    t - Snap to top of current page
    J/K - Zoom out/in
    H/L - Goto the previous/next page
    s - Zoom to fit width
    a - Zoom to fit height
    r - Reload document if changed
    R - Open most recent document
    >/< - Rotate document clockwise/counter-clockwise
    D - Toggle dual-page mode
    p - Print document
